esoco-common 1.2.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
de.esoco.lib.datatype  
de.esoco.lib.math  
de.esoco.lib.model
The model package contains a set of interfaces and some base implementations of these that define simple data structures based on the DataModel interface.
de.esoco.lib.property
The property package contains mainly interfaces that define access to typical object properties like Editable or attributes like TextAttribute.
de.esoco.lib.text
The text package currently only contains a single class with a subset of text manipulations methods that are safe for use in a limited Java environment like the Javascript translation of GWT.
